Subject: drm/i915/cdclk: turn around i915_drv.h and intel_cdclk.h dependency
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: cce936f4fff736927ffd53a61d7b2c6a1064e0c5
